1002501.1000851.1000867.1000961.description=Divide and conquer: This multi-position cargo divider lets you customize Tacoma's truck bed for a wide range of needs:
•Works in harmony with Tacoma's deck rail system
•Allows separation of loads to prevent sliding/tumbling
•Lightweight, corrosion-resistant black powder-coated aluminum construction
•Rotates for various configurations, including lying flat above cargo
•Tested to withstand loads up to 400 lbs.

Cargo and load capacity limited by weight and distribution.
